{"tid":1551271,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【數據分折，重溫 ！】想自殺？想重刷首抽？入黎睇睇先！","createTime":"2019-09-08T02:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T15:48:44.000Z","uid":27814,"like":151,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0d97cd7e5444bfed250ddbb84e44e696f9c97b37","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:31:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鑑於大量自殺潮，想同大家重溫，此post發起人為會員#59224 林曉音</span></span><br />\n開係學術台 推左成晚都無人睇<br />\n決定開係其他台<br />\n<br />\n最近連登負能量比較多<br />\n出現咗好多留言不停鼓勵各位自殺，重新投胎搵過戶好人家<br />\n更加有巴打不幸身先士卒<br />\n不過口講無憑，自殺到底可唔可以成功改變命運呢？<br />\n我地冇辦法從已經過身嘅巴打攞料<br />\n不過我地可以運用統計學，估算各位投胎轉世成功機會有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，雖然人類分開唔同種族同民族，但佢地都係同一個物種<br />\n所以我地假設一個人死咗，下世仍然身為人類嘅話，都有機會投胎去世界各國<br />\n透過分析各國出生人口數目，就可以搵出投胎去某個國家嘅機會啦<br />\n雖然投胎去某個窮國唔代表下世一定係窮人，投胎去發達國家都唔代表下世一定飛黃騰達<br />\n但係一個人身處咩國家，大概代表到呢個人嘅生活水平同幸福程度<br />\n更重要嘅係，透過數據分析，各位可以搵到下世到底會去咗邊度<br />\n睇完之後先再衡量下值唔值得死都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，事不且遲，我地直接睇統計結果啦<br />\n下面所有數據都係由The World Factbook拎到，原文係英文。因為樓主趕住出post，排名太後嘅國家就懶得譯返漢字名，大家明就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215202_334d980100e9817ef1b53d2e71a3235a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215202_334d980100e9817ef1b53d2e71a3235a.jpg&h=42ae0b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215203_78ce91c3a1ee49784e8e02e9dd642c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215203_78ce91c3a1ee49784e8e02e9dd642c26.jpg&h=551ddca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215203_73f00cdac2696b15e67b7a26a5b397fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215203_73f00cdac2696b15e67b7a26a5b397fa.jpg&h=4a71e406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215204_fe728157a5a025ecf15cf39cccdf3260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215204_fe728157a5a025ecf15cf39cccdf3260.jpg&h=67ae9a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215204_ed5d0742f2cfc6aa2604689c9cf8fed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215204_ed5d0742f2cfc6aa2604689c9cf8fed7.jpg&h=161545a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntoo long didn't read？我黎同大家解釋一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前十名國家合計嘅投胎機率有54.25%，即係你下世有超過一半機會投胎係呢十個國家，而呢啲國家大多數唔係窮，就係貧富懸殊或者冇自由。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一名係印度，各位有17.92%機會做印度人</span><br />\n可以瘋狂食咖哩同去恆河沖屎水涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更重要嘅係印度種姓制度遺害極深，萬一你出身「賤民」種姓就慘過食十舊屎<br />\n再者印度女性地位非常低，投胎做咗印度妹就自求多福<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第二名就係偉大嘅中國，投胎機會達12.48%</span><br />\n詳細情況就唔多講啦，總之即使你地死咗，都仲有八份之一嘅機會共享中國人榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前十名國家當中只有美國投得過，但得3%投胎機會<br />\n搏唔搏得過就自己考慮下啦<br />\n不過你唔係投胎去到美國就一勞永逸，你估美國冇窮人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿，我地眼光放遠啲，睇到頭50個國家咁多。<br />\n佢地合計嘅投胎機率有86.1%，姐係你下世好有可能會係五十個國家嘅其中之一出世。<br />\n撇開前十名唔計，係頭50個國家入面，算得上發達國家嘅只有日本、法國、英國同德國<br />\n佢地加埋美國，總投胎機率都只有5.41%<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姐係你下世會有86.1% - 5.41% = 80.69%機會去咗落後國家，咁就一世</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以大家好唔好砍掉重練呢？<br />\n相信大家諗到呢步，人生路中一定好唔好彩，受咗好多苦。<br />\n嘅然係咁，點解你地仲想自殺呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地黎到今時今日都咁唔好彩，憑咩相信你投胎就會突然黎運，投去好國家呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n總而言之，投胎轉世涉及風險，下世有多過八成機會慘過而家，人生更可變得毫無價值。投胎未必一定有賺，反而可能會招致損失。<br />\n自殺前請三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4994bc23694b19b7c146e22eef6bcde57c8f5e00","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881b7b723d1fbc1ec64da5e2cd6441b31ebdce98","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:31:58.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5709ffb4cff7dbca6352940487332c39cfab77","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:32:20.000Z","msg":"8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540b1e8bc63bb7cb73a2fd51e4317d09e94fe96b","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e02789d8fb721824f82a1a328cd7b243db77d6","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9053cf02cb2646f343425bd65f263b3c2bfbdc3","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:33:08.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c80c515504a5b8361e1f132652cd74382b