ock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2356b47f7dda4228701b4dcb1c389a625318d270","tid":1551271,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！<br />\n連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n今日 下午 美國領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=af58c618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"b8a02386977d14b87913d916f03a0569f3d2e0a6","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91626852bba8e719048b7375ca8cd37d6b7234d7","tid":1551271,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"131e38cb6666e3c9f1aef05b964cc4ed3e308aef","tid":1551271,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"樓主應該開創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"根本係學術台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"之前開左<br />\n無乜人見到"},{"pid":"c2adaeed8e2fe4c591c4c9588555631a03932a0a","tid":1551271,"uid":27814,"like":0,"di